properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued February 7 at 4:23AM AKST until February 8 at 9:00PM AKST by NWS Anchorage, AK
properties.description:
The National Weather Service in Anchorage has issued a High Wind
Warning, which is in effect from 4 AM to 9 PM AKST Saturday.

* TIMING...Winds rapidly increasing after midnight tonight
tapering down late Saturday evening.

* WINDS...Southwest wind 35 to 45 mph with gusts to 75 mph expected.

* IMPACTS...High winds may move loose debris and may damage
property.
properties.instruction:
A high wind warning means a hazardous high wind event is expected
or occurring. People are urged to secure loose objects that could
be blown around or damaged by the wind.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 4 AM TO 9 PM AKST SATURDAY
